{"tid":1594790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手］down vote呢條仆街youtuber","createTime":"2019-09-25T17:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T23:46:26.000Z","uid":274907,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"86f564b7f1fea1796a2085145d9c701348904b21","tid":1594790,"uid":274907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RFwGqF3QlVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRFwGqF3QlVc&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=0477e13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RFwGqF3QlVc</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣Richard Scotford係fb指責佢扮記者，將真記者置於危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6akbZB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6akbZB8.png&h=f1502228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢九月買左機票尼香港話要睇下香港發生咩事，語帶輕鬆，仲係條片show自己係amazon買嘅假press螢光衣同自己print嘅假記者證。跟住話go get some fun。係Richard facebook同其他人筆戰話自己係尼experience some teargas。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w83kSXe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw83kSXe.png&h=e91b1e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢俾人鬧完而家好小器，不過佢本身都係中立L，而家藍色出返曬尼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MTpAaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MTpAaJ.png&h=db58d9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔識講，大家去Richard Facebook自己睇，佢而家YouTube channel第一條片有8千幾個like，down vote得四千幾個。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQFfGQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQFfGQ0.png&h=40c4dc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得俾個講英文嘅有咁多like就唔由佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔係睇曬成條片係唔會有view，大家唔洗驚俾左view佢"},{"pid":"987f447b0b5c19593e8de0d3ed843b3e122935fa","tid":1594790,"uid":274907,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDhYEDs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%